Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.33,0:00:09.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,NETFLIX オリジナルシリーズ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.42,0:00:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I've realized something.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.42,0:00:14.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アイコ）私 思ったの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.93,0:00:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Until now, Kanzaki,\Nyou've lied about many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.93,0:00:18.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,神崎(かんざき)君は今まで\Nたくさんのウソをついてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.89,0:00:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,About my body and my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.89,0:00:22.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この体のこと 脳のこと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.93,0:00:25.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダイバーのみんなにも\N隠し事をしてた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.94,0:00:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You've hidden things from the Divers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.10,0:00:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You probably have many other secrets, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.10,0:00:29.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,多分 ほかにも たくさん
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.52,0:00:30.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉(ゆうや)）それは…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.65,0:00:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.03,0:00:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I was made from your lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.03,0:00:36.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アイコ）\N私は あなたのウソで出来ている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.53,0:00:37.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.49,0:00:44.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,〜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.53,0:02:07.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,〜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.54,0:02:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I was made from your lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.54,0:02:12.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は あなたのウソで出来ている
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.96,0:02:13.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.63,0:02:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though my brain\Nis fake and artificial,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.63,0:02:18.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でもね\Nこの脳が偽物でも作り物でも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.22,0:02:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I still love Mom and Ryota.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.22,0:02:21.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は お母さんと亮太(りょうた)を愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.51,0:02:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,These feelings are not fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.51,0:02:25.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この気持ちは偽物なんかじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.02,0:02:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to save them both.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.02,0:02:28.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２人を助けたい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.89,0:02:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to return this body\Nto the other me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.89,0:02:31.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう１人の私に この体を返したい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.15,0:02:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,She intends to sacrifice her own life\Nto put an end to all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.15,0:02:36.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彼女は自分の命と引き換えに\Nすべてを終わらせる気でいる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.53,0:02:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But that is my role.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.53,0:02:39.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも それは私の役目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.61,0:02:40.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,橘(たちばな)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.74,0:02:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Tachibana.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.45,0:02:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That is not my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.45,0:02:43.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは私の名前じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.95,0:02:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There is only one Aiko Tachibana.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.95,0:02:45.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,橘アイコは１人でいいの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.74,0:02:49.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉）\N君は… 君はそれでいいのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.75,0:02:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you want to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.00,0:02:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you asking?\NIsn't that what you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.00,0:02:53.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アイコ）\Nどうして？\Nそれがあなたの望みなんでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.63,0:02:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't hurry, the other me--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.63,0:02:55.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,早くしないと もう１人の私が…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.88,0:02:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on! I--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.88,0:02:58.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉）待ってくれ 僕は\N（アイコ）神崎君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.71,0:02:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-Kanzaki--\N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.34,0:02:59.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,違う！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.34,0:03:00.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.13,0:03:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not Yuya Kanzaki, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.13,0:03:04.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕もまた 神崎雄哉じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.60,0:03:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.60,0:03:08.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（伊佐津(いさづ)）さあ 始めようか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.06,0:03:10.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（竹原(たけはら)）待ってください
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.23,0:03:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.14,0:03:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.14,0:03:13.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,邪魔をしないでくれないか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.15,0:03:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.15,0:03:14.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Isazu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:15.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（佐保(さほ)）伊佐津先生\N（竹原）あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.65,0:03:18.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,佐保君？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.73,0:03:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Saho?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.69,0:03:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it really okay to do this, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.94,0:03:22.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（佐保）\N先生 本当に大丈夫ですか？\Nこんなことをなさって
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.66,0:03:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been proven\Nwe can establish a link.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.66,0:03:26.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（伊佐津）\Nリンクが張れることは実証済みだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.62,0:03:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.62,0:03:27.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それに
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.33,0:03:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuzuha is my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.33,0:03:30.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,柚葉(ゆずは)は私の娘だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.79,0:03:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuzuha?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.79,0:03:32.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（竹原）柚葉ちゃん？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Saho, did you know about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:35.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい 佐保君\N君は何か知ってるのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.34,0:03:37.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ええ もちろん
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.42,0:03:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.71,0:03:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been with Yuzuha and Dr. Isazu\Nfor a long time, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.71,0:03:40.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は ずっと柚葉ちゃんと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.51,0:03:42.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,伊佐津先生のおそばに\Nおりましたから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.01,0:03:43.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.76,0:03:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only natural that I assist\Nin restoring Yuzuha's consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.76,0:03:48.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すべては柚葉ちゃんが目覚めるため\Nお手伝いは当然です
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.97,0:03:51.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（伊佐津）うっ うう…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.31,0:03:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Yuzuha. Lend me your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.31,0:03:55.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ 柚葉\N私に力を貸しておくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.04,0:04:13.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっ！ くっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.22,0:04:24.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うう…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.39,0:04:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I believed that my body and my life\Nwould last only until...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.39,0:04:38.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉）\N僕の この体 この命は\Nバーストを終息させるまでのもの
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.90,0:04:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the Burst is ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.90,0:04:40.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう思っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.61,0:04:41.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But, not you. You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:45.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも君はそうじゃない\Nもう…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:46.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（メキメキメキ…）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.78,0:04:47.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（２人）あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:50.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（２人）はっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.33,0:04:53.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（２人）あっ…うっ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.50,0:04:58.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（２人）あっ…えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.92,0:05:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.92,0:05:00.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（伊佐津）アイコ君\N（２人）あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.25,0:05:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.25,0:05:01.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（黒瀬(くろせ)）なに！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.05,0:05:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no need to sacrifice yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.05,0:05:04.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（伊佐津）\N君が犠牲になる必要はないんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.13,0:05:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You are undoubtedly one of a kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.13,0:05:07.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君は れっきとした１人の人間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.30,0:05:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Isazu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.30,0:05:09.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春(こはる)）伊佐津博士？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.97,0:05:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he controlling the Matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.97,0:05:12.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヤツがマターを操ってるってのか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no reason for you\Nto get caught up in his obsession
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:17.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その男の妄執に巻き込まれ\N人の姿を失うことなどない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.44,0:05:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and lose your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.27,0:05:19.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（２人）うっ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.73,0:05:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can put your life to much better use.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.73,0:05:24.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私なら もっときちんと\N君の命を使ってあげられる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.65,0:05:26.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉）うわっ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:28.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アイコ）神崎君！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.20,0:05:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.49,0:05:30.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,神崎君！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.62,0:05:31.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.66,0:05:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This Matter is from the duplicate bodies
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.66,0:05:35.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（伊佐津）\Nこのマターたちは貴様の作品である
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.29,0:05:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you created using Cell Assembler Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.29,0:05:38.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,セル･アセンブラ２によって\N作られた複製体
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.08,0:05:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They just don't have functioning brains.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.08,0:05:41.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ脳が機能できなかっただけ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.92,0:05:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're all my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.92,0:05:43.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すべて私の娘だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.59,0:05:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even now, their minds are connected\Nto my comatose daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.59,0:05:48.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今も眠ったままの柚葉の心と\Nつながっている
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.84,0:05:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To return Yuzuha to consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.84,0:05:52.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,柚葉が真に目覚めるためには
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.31,0:05:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aiko Tachibana,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.31,0:05:53.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,橘アイコ君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.81,0:05:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must have\Nyour artificial organism brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.81,0:05:57.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君の人工生体脳が\Nどうしても必要なのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.39,0:05:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,My brain?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.39,0:05:59.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アイコ）わ… 私の？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.15,0:06:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You see,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.15,0:06:00.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（伊佐津）\Nそうとも
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.94,0:06:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the only brain ever regenerated,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.94,0:06:03.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,脳神経組織の再生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.44,0:06:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}or should I say,\Nthe only successfully created brain...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.44,0:06:07.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや 新生に成功した ただ一つの例
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.11,0:06:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.11,0:06:09.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが君だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.74,0:06:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will probe your brain at the\Nmolecular level to discover its secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.74,0:06:12.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君の脳を分子レベルまで\Nかき分けて
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:14.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は その秘密を突き止める
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.58,0:06:15.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:17.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんてこと
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.83,0:06:21.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,由良(ゆら)と伊佐津は 今まで\Nあの子の脳みそを奪い合って
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.04,0:06:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Yura and Isazu\Nhave been fighting to get her brain?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.21,0:06:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.21,0:06:23.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう… なるな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.09,0:06:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You monsters! Grown men\Nfighting over a young girl's brain?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.13,0:06:27.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカなの！\Nあんな女の子に いい大人が
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.55,0:06:28.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.38,0:06:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You succeeded in bringing to life
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.38,0:06:33.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（伊佐津）\N史上初めて実用化された人工生体脳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.43,0:06:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}an artificial organism brain\Nfor the first time in history.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.43,0:06:37.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは今まで その可能性だけが\N一人歩きしてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.73,0:06:40.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,由良ノートの成果\N違うか？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.73,0:06:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is this all recorded in the Yura Notes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.02,0:06:41.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くっ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.02,0:06:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tell me! What is the secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.02,0:06:44.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（伊佐津）\N言え！ その正体は何だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.27,0:06:45.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アイコ）いやあ！\N（雄哉）あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:48.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぐっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:51.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.16,0:06:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Tachibana!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.45,0:06:53.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉）橘！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.66,0:06:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't kill her.\NI don't want her to hear this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.66,0:06:57.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（伊佐津）\N殺しはしない\N彼女に聞かせたい話でもないだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:06:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All right, tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.33,0:06:59.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ 答えろ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.42,0:07:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Cell Assembler...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.42,0:07:03.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,セル･アセンブラ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.21,0:07:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.21,0:07:06.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３だ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.21,0:07:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Three?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.34,0:07:08.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ？ ３だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.55,0:07:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.80,0:07:10.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.34,0:07:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean you upgraded the Cell Assembler?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.34,0:07:13.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,セル･アセンブラが\Nアップデートされていただと？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.80,0:07:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to Cell Assembler Two,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.80,0:07:16.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,セル･アセンブラ２によって
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.14,0:07:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,resilient cells were able to\Nreproduce rapidly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.14,0:07:19.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,迅速かつ強靭(きょうじん)な\N再生能力を得た細胞は
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.64,0:07:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They couldn't be damaged or degraded.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.64,0:07:21.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,傷つくことも老いることもない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.85,0:07:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But, that wasn't enough to make a brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.85,0:07:26.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも それだけじゃ\N脳を作ることはできなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.82,0:07:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A brain develops
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.82,0:07:27.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,脳の発達は
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.07,0:07:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,by eliminating\Npreviously established connections.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.07,0:07:31.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すでに あるつながりが\N消えることによって起こる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.70,0:07:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Early on in development,\Nrandomly created connections
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.70,0:07:35.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,発達の初期段階で\N無作為に生じたつながりは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.28,0:07:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,are soon selectively destroyed,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.28,0:07:37.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やがて選択的に消滅し
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.62,0:07:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and a refined network grows.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.62,0:07:40.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,洗練されたネットワークへと\N成長していく
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.37,0:07:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.37,0:07:42.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（伊佐津）\Nそんなことは分かっている
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.75,0:07:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Theoretically, artificial reproduction\Nof a human personality
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.87,0:07:46.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが その過程は\N高い不確定性に支配される
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}capable of controlling\Nsuch a highly uncertain process--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.04,0:07:49.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,特定の人格の完全複製など\N原理的に…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:51.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉）不可能だった\N（伊佐津）うっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.30,0:07:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Was impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:53.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから僕は
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,after I accelerated network creation\Nto be as fast as possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:57.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ネットワークの形成速度を\N極限まで高めたあと
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.31,0:07:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I waited...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.64,0:07:58.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待った
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.60,0:07:59.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.60,0:08:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}until the person\Ncalled Aiko Tachibana emerged.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.60,0:08:03.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉）橘アイコと呼べるものが\Nそこに出現するまで
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.73,0:08:04.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（伊佐津）\Nありえない！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.23,0:08:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That would take as long\Nas the evolution of life itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.23,0:08:09.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それでは生命の進化と\N同じ時間がかかってしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.90,0:08:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,As I developed Cell Assembler Two,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.90,0:08:13.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉）\Nだからこそ僕は\Nセル･アセンブラ２と並行して
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.03,0:08:16.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ドリームコンタクトの技術を\N開発した
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.16,0:08:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I also developed Dream Contact technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.74,0:08:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dream Contact?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.74,0:08:19.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（伊佐津）\Nドリームコンタクト
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Like you said,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:21.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉）あなたの言うとおり
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.58,0:08:25.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,脳の形成は\N生命進化の過程とよく似ている
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.71,0:08:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,brain formation resembles\Nthe evolution of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.83,0:08:27.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自然選択に任せれば
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.17,0:08:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,To proceed naturally,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.09,0:08:33.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,任意の状態の脳の複製には\N無限に等しいプロセスが必要だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.21,0:08:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}an emulation of\Ninfinite possibilities is needed
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.84,0:08:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to duplicate a mind\Nwith a will of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.84,0:08:37.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,けれど オリジナルの\N橘アイコの脳活性状態は
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was able to perfectly monitor\Nthe brain activity
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.85,0:08:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}of the original Aiko Tachibana.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.85,0:08:40.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,完璧にモニター できていた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.35,0:08:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The goal was in sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.35,0:08:42.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ゴールは見えていたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.43,0:08:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I repeatedly did the reverse calculations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.43,0:08:45.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから僕は\Nそこから逆算した結果を重ねた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.52,0:08:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All the unlimited divergent possibilities\Ncancelled each other out and optimized.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.52,0:08:51.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無限に発散するはずの可能性は\N互いに打ち消し合い 最適化され
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.82,0:08:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In a surprisingly short time,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.98,0:08:53.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,驚くほど短時間で
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.86,0:08:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}an artificial brain that could be called\NAiko Tachibana came into existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.86,0:08:58.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人工生体脳は\N橘アイコという状態へと収束した
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.95,0:09:02.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんたの相棒\Nちょっと魔物じみてる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.08,0:09:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Your friend is a bit of a mad scientist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.08,0:09:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That mad scientist is our only hope now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.08,0:09:05.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今はその魔物だけが希望だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.83,0:09:07.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バースト終息の可能性は まだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.00,0:09:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He can still stop the Burst.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.96,0:09:10.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アラーム）\N（２人）あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.30,0:09:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As I'm sure you can see,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.59,0:09:12.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アナウンサー）\Nご覧いただけますでしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.71,0:09:14.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,マリグナント･エリア焼灼(しょうしゃく)に向け
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.76,0:09:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the reinforcements at Camp Toyama
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.92,0:09:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}are leaving the base, and heading out\Nto incinerate the Malignant Matter Area.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.92,0:09:19.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここ富山駐屯地に集結していた\N増派部隊も次々と出発していきます
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.47,0:09:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All Self-Defense Forces branches\Nare being concentrated
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.01,0:09:24.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,政府は陸海空自衛隊の総力を結集し
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.18,0:09:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}for a decisive strike\Nto end the crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.35,0:09:27.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一気に事態の収束を図る構えです
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.64,0:09:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,MALIGNANT AREA\NTO BE INCINERATED
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.77,0:09:29.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.98,0:09:32.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あああああ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.57,0:09:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fine!\NI acknowledge your godlike abilities!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.57,0:09:36.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前の手は神の手だ！\N認めよう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.45,0:09:38.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが それをあるべきところへ返せ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.45,0:09:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But things must return\Nto where they belong!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.03,0:09:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Return gods to the gods!\NReturn Yuzuha to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.03,0:09:41.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,神の手は神に！\N柚葉は私に！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.41,0:09:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Back to the gods with you, Toshihide Yura!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:45.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,神の御許へゆけよ\N由良俊英(としひで)！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.29,0:09:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Know Yuzuha's pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.29,0:09:49.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,柚葉の苦しみを知れ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.83,0:09:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Be punished for preventing\Nher from waking up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.83,0:09:52.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,目覚めを妨げた報いを受けろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.67,0:09:55.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.76,0:09:56.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アイコ）はっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.22,0:10:03.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（グミ）キュイ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.68,0:10:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Gummi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.68,0:10:04.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グミ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.10,0:10:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.10,0:10:07.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここは どこ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.85,0:10:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the other me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.85,0:10:09.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう１人の私の…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.02,0:10:14.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（すすり泣き）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:15.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アイコ）誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.99,0:10:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.99,0:10:18.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,女の子？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.61,0:10:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Which body should I go back to?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.61,0:10:21.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（柚葉）どの体に戻ればいいの？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is she crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:23.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アイコ）何？ 何を泣いてるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to get out of here. Tell me how.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:27.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（柚葉）教えて ここから出たいの
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.79,0:10:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Dad. Don't hurt Dr. Yura.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.79,0:10:30.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お父さん やめて\N由良先生を…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.67,0:10:31.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.79,0:10:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yura? Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.79,0:10:34.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,由良？ ねえ 待って！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.92,0:10:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't hurt him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.92,0:10:36.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（柚葉）お願い 先生を
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.05,0:10:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait! What's happening to Kanzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.05,0:10:39.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ねえ 待って！\N神崎君がどうしたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.38,0:10:41.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（柚葉）殺さないで！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.39,0:10:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.35,0:10:44.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.73,0:10:55.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（一樹(かずき)）\Nアイコちゃん アイコちゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.81,0:10:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Aiko! Aiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.19,0:10:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.19,0:10:58.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一樹君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.57,0:11:00.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（一樹）よかった　はっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.74,0:11:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.83,0:11:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-Kanzaki!\N-This way! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.99,0:11:05.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（一樹）神崎！\N（雄哉）こっちだ 早く！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.83,0:11:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.83,0:11:07.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アイコ）神崎君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.87,0:11:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to jump, Aiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.87,0:11:09.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（一樹）飛ぶよ アイコちゃん\N（アイコ）え？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.67,0:11:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take a magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.67,0:11:15.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉）マガジン もらう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.46,0:11:17.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この階段を下るんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.55,0:11:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Take these stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.01,0:11:20.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,早く！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.05,0:11:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.34,0:11:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Self-Defense Forces will attack soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.34,0:11:26.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（伊佐津）\N自衛隊が総攻撃の準備に入った
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.51,0:11:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no way you can accomplish\Nwhat you came to do, Yura.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.51,0:11:30.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,由良 貴様の目的は\Nもう果たされることはない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.94,0:11:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Give it all up! Get in the shelter!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.94,0:11:33.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すべてを中止し シェルターに入れ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.02,0:11:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Obey me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.02,0:11:35.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私に従え！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.78,0:11:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Director!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.78,0:11:43.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（堀(ほり)）局長！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.53,0:11:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,All AMBREC companies\Nannounced they'll cancel
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.53,0:11:47.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アメビレック関連企業が\N足並み そろえて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.28,0:11:49.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,知財権の独占提供を打ち切ると
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.29,0:11:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,our exclusive use\Nof their technologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.87,0:11:53.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,総攻撃になれば\N最先端技術が ごっそり国外に
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.91,0:11:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If the attack proceeds,\Nall that science will go abroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.63,0:11:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-Not yet.\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.71,0:11:54.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（南原(なんばら)）まだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.75,0:11:55.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.42,0:11:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We can stall this a little bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.42,0:11:59.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ少しは時間を稼げるはず
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.13,0:12:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hori.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.55,0:12:00.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,堀君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:01.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.26,0:12:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a favor to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.26,0:12:04.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたにお願いがあるの
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.77,0:12:12.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アイコ）きゃあ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.98,0:12:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.98,0:12:14.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉）しまった！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.15,0:12:22.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（２人）え？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.03,0:12:26.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ　これって…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.99,0:12:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.99,0:12:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try to suppress the Matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.99,0:12:29.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（橘アイコ）\N私がマターの体を押さえこんでみる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.58,0:12:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She's protecting us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.58,0:12:32.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,守ってくれてるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.37,0:12:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Protecting us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.37,0:12:33.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,守って？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:35.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（一樹）よし 行くよ\N（アイコ）え？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:36.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アイコ）うわっ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.89,0:12:48.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉）ぐは…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.26,0:12:49.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（２人）え？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.39,0:12:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Tachibana okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.39,0:12:50.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉）橘は無事か？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.18,0:12:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.39,0:12:52.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無事なんだな？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.56,0:12:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yes, she's fine!\N-Kanzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.64,0:12:54.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（一樹）ああ 大丈夫だ\N（アイコ）神崎君！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.39,0:12:58.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉）\N右に折れた突き当たりの部屋へ！\N僕もすぐに行く
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.52,0:12:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn right. It's the last room!\NI'll be there soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.57,0:13:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I will protect...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.57,0:13:06.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕が橘アイコを
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.99,0:13:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Tachibana Aiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.99,0:13:09.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,守る！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.08,0:13:14.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（荒い息）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.33,0:13:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.54,0:13:15.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アイコ）神崎君！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.12,0:13:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.12,0:13:17.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（一樹）神崎！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.17,0:13:23.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（一樹）ハア…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.13,0:13:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't the shelter, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.13,0:13:29.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シェルターじゃないよな？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.39,0:13:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a medicinal warehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.39,0:13:31.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉）薬剤保管庫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.68,0:13:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty sturdy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.68,0:13:34.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,多少は頑丈だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.10,0:13:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanzaki, I saw a girl inside the Matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.10,0:13:41.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,神崎君 私 マターの中で\N女の子を見たの
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.27,0:13:43.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,女の子？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.28,0:13:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,A girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.94,0:13:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,She was a pretty girl with long hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.94,0:13:46.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,髪の長い きれいな子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.15,0:13:48.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“ここから出して”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.16,0:13:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She wanted to get out,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.95,0:13:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and asked which body to go back to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.95,0:13:51.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“どの体に戻ればいいの？”って
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.74,0:13:52.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Where should I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:55.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（柚葉）\N私は どこに行けばいいの？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.79,0:13:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that's what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.83,0:13:58.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そういうことか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.33,0:14:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing? What's your plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.33,0:14:02.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（一樹）\Nおい 何してんだ\Nどうする気だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.05,0:14:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Aiko. Let's get to the shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.05,0:14:08.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アイコちゃん 行こう\Nシェルターに避難するんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.59,0:14:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Aiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.59,0:14:10.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アイコちゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.68,0:14:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I'm not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.68,0:14:14.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アイコ）\Nごめんなさい　私 行けない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.35,0:14:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not? I don't want you to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.60,0:14:17.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして？\N俺は君を死なせたくないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I met you,\Nwhen my arm was grabbed by the Matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:25.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君と出会う前\N俺はマターに腕をつかまれて
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.82,0:14:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw a vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.82,0:14:27.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,幻を見た
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.15,0:14:27.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.53,0:14:32.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.21,0:14:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a happy family.\NA traffic accident. The Burst.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.21,0:14:44.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,幸せそうな家族\N交通事故 バースト
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.55,0:14:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.55,0:14:45.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今なら分かる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.42,0:14:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Those were your memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.42,0:14:49.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれは君の記憶なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.68,0:14:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.68,0:14:52.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は君を救いたい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.51,0:14:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how hard things get,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.51,0:14:54.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君がどんなにつらくても
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.22,0:14:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear I'll be by your side!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.22,0:14:57.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が絶対 一緒にいる！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.61,0:15:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazuki, that was not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.61,0:15:06.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一樹君 それは私じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.28,0:15:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's memories of the other me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.28,0:15:09.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう１人の私の記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.15,0:15:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.40,0:15:10.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.11,0:15:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.11,0:15:13.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは私じゃないの
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.16,0:15:15.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ　くっ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.91,0:15:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't understand it! How can that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.91,0:15:18.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かんないよ どうして
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.29,0:15:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I love...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.29,0:15:20.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は君が…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.33,0:15:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in love with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.33,0:15:24.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が好きなのは 君なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.67,0:15:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.67,0:15:28.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがとう　でも…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.05,0:15:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.30,0:15:31.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（一樹）言うなよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.39,0:15:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me your gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.39,0:15:37.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉）銃を貸してくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.97,0:15:39.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（一樹）ハア
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.31,0:15:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This will cause an explosion\Nwhen ignited.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.56,0:15:42.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉）着火すれば\N爆発的燃焼を起こす
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.98,0:15:45.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ドアと外のマターを吹き飛ばして\N道を開く
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.02,0:15:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll blow a path\Nthrough the door and the Matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.61,0:15:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.61,0:15:47.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふざけんな！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.69,0:15:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. Shoot it, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.69,0:15:51.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉）\Nそうか　なら 君が撃ってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.53,0:15:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Get down as soon as you pull the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.53,0:15:53.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,引き金を引いたら\Nすぐに体を伏せるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.57,0:15:56.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,神崎！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.78,0:15:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.28,0:15:58.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺には分かる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.29,0:15:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I can sense it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.95,0:16:02.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前だって アイコちゃんのこと\N何とも思ってないわけがない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.08,0:16:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you have feelings for Aiko, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.92,0:16:04.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それでも行くのかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.04,0:16:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But you'll still do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.88,0:16:07.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それでもアイコちゃんに\Nマターになれって言うのかよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.88,0:16:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You still plan on turning her\Ninto the Matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.00,0:16:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you toss her aside\Nand tell her to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.21,0:16:10.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人を捨てて\N消えろって言うのかよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.68,0:16:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.68,0:16:16.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一樹君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.55,0:16:21.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私のことを思ってくれるなら\Nどうか救ってください
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.56,0:16:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If you love me, then save them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.35,0:16:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Aiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.35,0:16:23.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（一樹）アイコちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.23,0:16:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Not my body or my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.23,0:16:26.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この体でも 脳でもない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.52,0:16:29.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お母さんと亮太を助けたい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.61,0:16:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Save my Mom and Ryota.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.90,0:16:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart demands it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.94,0:16:32.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう叫び続けてる この心を！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.78,0:16:33.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.99,0:16:42.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うおおおお！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.93,0:17:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Tank and artillery battalions will\Ncommence firing at 8:00 p.m. as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.93,0:17:04.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（第三部長）\N戦車大隊 特科大隊 予定どおり
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.69,0:17:06.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２０:００(フタマルマルマル)時より射撃を開始します
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.19,0:17:17.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（第二部長）\Nエリア内に民間人の侵入者 多数
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.24,0:17:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There are numerous\Ncivilian trespassers in the Area.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.78,0:17:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,All units, hold your fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.78,0:17:21.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（師団長）各部隊 射撃待て
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.39,0:17:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.39,0:17:40.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたって人は…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.69,0:17:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Explain yourself, Nanbara!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.85,0:17:47.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（大臣）説明しろ 南原
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.56,0:17:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I exercised my right as Director\Nto lift the Malignant Area blockade.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.69,0:17:50.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,局長権限で
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.23,0:17:52.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,マリグナント･エリアの封鎖を\N解除しました
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.07,0:17:54.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何のつもりか！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.23,0:17:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,For what reason?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.03,0:17:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Since Matter activity\Nin Area Four has ceased,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.03,0:17:58.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,エリア４までのマターが\N不活性した現在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.20,0:18:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided that securing samples\Nthere took priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.20,0:18:01.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,サンプル保全作業を\N優先すべきと判断しました
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.78,0:18:03.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くっ… 貴様
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.62,0:18:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.33,0:18:07.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,エリア内の対処は\N一任を受けたはずですが
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.54,0:18:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I was given\Ncomplete authority over the Area.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.83,0:18:10.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふざけるな！\Nダイバーどもは撤収
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.04,0:18:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough!\NRecall those Divers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.46,0:18:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're relieved of your post immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.46,0:18:13.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様は この場で解任 更迭だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.56,0:18:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't want to go down with her,\Ntell me everything she knows!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.56,0:18:27.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,共倒れが嫌なら
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.27,0:18:30.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの女の握っていたものを\Nすべて吐き出せ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.27,0:18:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Write a report immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.27,0:18:32.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,報告をまとめてこい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.86,0:18:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hello? Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.86,0:18:40.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（黒瀬）はい どなた？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.32,0:18:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nanbara asked me to call.\NMy name is Hori. I work for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.32,0:18:44.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（堀）\N南原の指示でご連絡しました\N部下の堀と申します
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.66,0:18:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You work for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.70,0:18:45.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,南原の？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.95,0:18:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.95,0:18:47.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（堀）\N用件だけ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.29,0:18:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The attack on the Area has been postponed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.29,0:18:49.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,エリアへの総攻撃は 一時中止です
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.42,0:18:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.42,0:18:51.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだって？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.63,0:18:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Director has bought you time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.63,0:18:53.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（堀）\N局長が時間を稼ぎました
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.71,0:18:56.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか あいつはどうしてる？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.88,0:18:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. What happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.55,0:19:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She has sacrificed everything\Nshe worked for, her entire career,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.55,0:19:00.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（堀）\Nあの人はご自分のすべてともいえる\Nキャリアと引き換えに
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.72,0:19:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to stop the attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.72,0:19:02.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,攻撃を止めてみせた
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.18,0:19:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.18,0:19:04.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お… おい まさか！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.89,0:19:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She constantly spoke about\Nthe interests of the nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.89,0:19:08.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（堀）\N二言目には 国益 国益と\Nうるさい人でしたが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.77,0:19:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've never seen anyone sacrifice\Nso much for something
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.77,0:19:12.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな不確かなものに\Nあそこまで殉じられる人を
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.15,0:19:13.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕は知らない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.31,0:19:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so abstract.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.98,0:19:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The attack would only make\Nthe Burst worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.98,0:19:17.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,総攻撃は むしろ\Nバーストを悪化させるだけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.24,0:19:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Your boss did the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.24,0:19:20.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんたのボスは正しかった
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.24,0:19:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She'll be rewarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.24,0:19:22.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（堀）\N報われます
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.70,0:19:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The attack has been postponed.\NInform Yura.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.70,0:19:28.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,攻撃は中止だ\N由良に知らせてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.41,0:19:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.41,0:19:29.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無理でしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.62,0:19:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We can see Research Facility Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.62,0:19:33.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,第二研内部のモニターは\Nできてるけど
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.54,0:19:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we contact them,\NIsazu will find out, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.54,0:19:37.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（黒瀬）\Nこっちから呼びかけたら\N伊佐津にも知られちまうってことか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.97,0:19:44.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.01,0:19:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.72,0:19:47.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.48,0:19:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.48,0:19:52.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.86,0:19:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it broken?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.19,0:19:56.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉）故障？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.15,0:19:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's saying something.\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.23,0:19:58.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（一樹）何か しゃべってる\N（雄哉）え？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.48,0:20:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,"Yuya, come in."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.48,0:20:00.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（一樹）“雄哉 応答せよ”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.32,0:20:01.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アイコ）え？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.36,0:20:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurose?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.36,0:20:02.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉）黒瀬さん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.24,0:20:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Visible light communication?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.53,0:20:05.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,可視光通信か
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.74,0:20:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We got through!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.74,0:20:07.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,通じたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.79,0:20:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's answering!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.79,0:20:10.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,返信だ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.08,0:20:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.46,0:20:12.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,読むわ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.66,0:20:17.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“柚葉ちゃんと彼女の複製体との\Nリンクを切れ”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.67,0:20:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,"Cut the link between Yuzuha\Nand her duplicate bodies."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.13,0:20:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.17,0:20:19.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なに？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.21,0:20:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Link?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.50,0:20:20.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,リンク？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.72,0:20:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The comatose girl\Nis linked to her duplicate bodies?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.88,0:20:23.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,意識不明の子と複製体が\Nつながってるってこと？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.43,0:20:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Isazu is trying to return Yuzuha\Nto consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.43,0:20:27.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,伊佐津が柚葉ちゃんの意識を\N取り戻そうとして
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.68,0:20:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He's trying to physically sync\Nher with her duplicate bodies' brains.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.76,0:20:31.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彼女の複製体の脳と\N物理的に同期を図ろうとしたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.31,0:20:36.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１つも成功しなかったのに\Nそんなもん まだつなげてたのか！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.35,0:20:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}None of them succeeded.\NSo why were they still connected?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.06,0:20:39.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）\Nじゃあ リンクを切るってのは？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.11,0:20:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, how do we cut the link?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.82,0:20:41.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,桐生(きりゅう)病院
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.94,0:20:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,At Kiryu Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.57,0:20:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It means we sneak in\Nright under Isazu's nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.57,0:20:44.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,伊佐津のお膝元に\N潜り込めってことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.41,0:20:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Three blocks to Primary Point.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.41,0:20:49.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（白石(しらいし)）\Nプライマリー･ポイントまで\N３ブロック
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.87,0:20:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But no sign of\Nthe two people we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.87,0:20:51.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（遙香(はるか)）\Nでも肝心の２人が見当たらない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.50,0:20:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-Seri!\N-Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.50,0:20:54.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（白石）芹(せり)さん！\N（遙香）しまった！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.25,0:21:00.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（２人）え？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.55,0:21:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaede!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.55,0:21:04.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（遙香）楓(かえで)！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.30,0:21:06.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楓）ヘヘッ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.55,0:21:09.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつらが迷子になってんなら
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.64,0:21:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If they're lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.51,0:21:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll just have to bring them\Nto their objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.51,0:21:13.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（相模(さがみ)）\N俺たちが目的地から\N出迎えに行ってやろうじゃねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.02,0:21:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a purpose to what we're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.02,0:21:17.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この道行きに意味はある
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.48,0:21:18.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（２人）あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.32,0:21:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.32,0:21:22.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ええ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.74,0:21:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,RECALL THE SELF-DEFENSE FORCES!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.40,0:21:27.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（堀）\N御社をはじめとする\Nアメビレックの存続こそ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.70,0:21:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The existence of your company\Nand AMBREC itself
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.57,0:21:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,is in the national interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.57,0:21:29.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,国益そのものです
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.57,0:21:31.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,希望はまだあります
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.58,0:21:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There is still hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.29,0:21:33.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（伊佐津）由良…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.33,0:21:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yura...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.95,0:21:35.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,由良〜！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.12,0:21:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yura!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.58,0:21:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.58,0:21:38.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう やめてください
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.17,0:21:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't interfere, Takehara!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.29,0:21:40.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,竹原さん 邪魔をしないでください
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.88,0:21:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an official operation!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.88,0:21:43.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これは正式なオペなんですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.17,0:21:45.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.26,0:21:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Primary Point.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.26,0:21:50.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉）\Nここがプライマリー･ポイントだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.14,0:21:52.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アイコ）え？\N（一樹）ここが？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.31,0:21:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-What?\N-Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.68,0:21:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The multipurpose surgical installation\NALSUS is in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.68,0:21:57.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉）\N多目的手術装置アルサスは\Nこの中にある
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.19,0:22:00.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.36,0:22:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.86,0:22:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I know this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.86,0:22:12.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アイコ）ここは… 私 知ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.45,0:22:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen it many times\Nin my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.45,0:22:15.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何度も夢に出てきた場所だ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.30,0:22:29.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉）あ…\N（一樹･アイコ）あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.93,0:22:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This is ALSUS?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.93,0:22:36.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（一樹）これがアルサス？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.40,0:22:47.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,〜
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.60,0:24:09.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,〜
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.78,0:24:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Subtitle translation by Brian Athey
